rows.label: tlk45600171_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Ahahahaha... Finally I am here!
The Acedian cathedral...it's everything
I imagined! One gigantic work of art!

rows.label: tlk45600171_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I told my husband in Avaritia I had
an "important trade deal" to negotiate.
He'd never have let me visit otherwise!

rows.label: tlk45600171_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Ahh, I wonder how much the carvings
on a single pillar here are worth?

rows.label: tlk45600171_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Oh, but that's the merchant in me
talking! Silly me...you can't put a price
on this kind of magnificent artwork!
